<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 01:08:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>法学硕士建筑画廊</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/llm-architecture-gallery</link><description>一个画廊，收集来自大型 LLM 架构比较和相关文章的架构数据，并附有情况说明书和原始部分的链接。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/llm-architecture-gallery2.webp" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 01:08:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/llm-architecture-gallery</guid></item><item><title>新抗原及其在肿瘤免疫治疗中的潜在应用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/neoantigens-and-their-potential-applications-in-tumor-immunotherapy</link><description>恶性肿瘤的发病率正在增加，其中大多数与全世界的高发病率和死亡率有关。恶性肿瘤的传统治疗方法是手术，加上放疗或化疗。然而，这些治疗策略经常伴随着不良副作用。近几十年来，肿瘤免疫疗法在治疗癌症方面显示出显着疗效。随着测序技术和生物信息学算法的发展，新抗原由于高水平的免疫原性而成为癌症免疫治疗的引人注目的靶标。此外，基于新抗原的疫苗已显示出用于癌症治疗的潜力，主要是通过增强 T 细胞反应。新抗原也被证明在免疫检查点阻断疗法中有效。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/neoantigens-and-their-potential-applications-in-tumor-immunotherapy.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 00:53:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/neoantigens-and-their-potential-applications-in-tumor-immunotherapy</guid></item><item><title>地球和月球上无碳能源的金属燃料</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/metal-fuel-for-carbon-free-energy-on-earth-and-the-moon</link><description>太空发射的生态解决方案之一是“房间里的大象”。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/metal-fuel-for-carbon-free-energy-on-earth-and-the-moon.gif" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 00:38:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/metal-fuel-for-carbon-free-energy-on-earth-and-the-moon</guid></item><item><title>纳米技术：建造最小规模的机器</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/nanotechnology-building-machines-at-the-smallest-scale</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 00:23:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/nanotechnology-building-machines-at-the-smallest-scale</guid></item><item><title>注意力机制：概述</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/attention-mechanism-overview</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 00:08:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/attention-mechanism-overview</guid></item><item><title>轨道农场</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/orbital-farms</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 23:53:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/orbital-farms</guid></item><item><title>前往并输入</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/go-to-and-enter</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 23:38:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/go-to-and-enter</guid></item><item><title>Cyborgian：从这里获取你的人工智能职业生存指南：👉顶级未来学家 Ray Kurzweil</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/cyborgian-grab-your-ai-career-survivial-guide-from-here-%f0%9f%91%89-top-futurist-ray-kurzweil</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 23:23:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/cyborgian-grab-your-ai-career-survivial-guide-from-here-%f0%9f%91%89-top-futurist-ray-kurzweil</guid></item><item><title>利用细菌将塑料瓶转化为帕金森氏症药物</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/plastic-bottles-transformed-into-parkinsons-drug-using-bacteria</link><description>一项研究表明，一种治疗帕金森病的药物可以采用一种开创性的方法，用废塑料瓶制成。该方法利用细菌的力量将消费后的塑料转化为左旋多巴，这是一种治疗神经系统疾病的一线药物。研究人员表示，这是第一次通过自然生物过程将塑料废物转化为神经系统疾病的治疗方法。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/plastic-bottles-transformed-into-parkinsons-drug-using-bacteria2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 23:08:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/plastic-bottles-transformed-into-parkinsons-drug-using-bacteria</guid></item><item><title>基于超声波的技术可将大量治疗药物输送到癌细胞中</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/ultrasound-based-technology-to-deliver-large-therapeutics-into-cancer-cells</link><description>在这项研究中，作者为这些微泡配备了合成核酸链，旨在与癌细胞而非健康细胞细胞膜上出现的特定生化受体结合。然后，他们尝试了几种超声波频率和强度的组合，以找到打开细胞膜上的孔以允许 PROTAC 进入的完美配对。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ultrasound-based-technology-to-deliver-large-therapeutics-into-cancer-cells2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 22:53:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/ultrasound-based-technology-to-deliver-large-therapeutics-into-cancer-cells</guid></item></channel></rss>